{"tid":464642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要人愛你首先要愛自己","createTime":"2017-11-10T16:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T10:49:33.000Z","uid":148485,"like":87,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d56c041194e294bbea531b20c8dbcf788ab86edc","tid":464642,"uid":148485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:55:08.000Z","msg":"要愛自己，錫自己。<br />\n唔可以將對方擺做生活重心；<br />\n唔可以睇得對方咁重要。<br />\n要對自己更好。<br />\n呢個世界無話邊個無咗邊個唔得，<br />\n除咗自己，無人會願意無條件咁對自己好。<br />\n<br />\n我全部都知全部都明，但硬係做唔到"},{"pid":"7808741eee3f17601a80b982af2cb671784783e9","tid":464642,"uid":148485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:57:44.000Z","msg":"要點先可以愛自己多啲？"},{"pid":"b8d71967bb04cfde79045698ccd3aacd0ed8a30f","tid":464642,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"3ea39bffd05a136803539454f6d9d5af32cb2c0f","tid":464642,"uid":148485,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"I've become so numb, I can't feel you there.<br />\nI've become so tired, so much more aware.<br />\nI'm becoming this,<br />\nAll I want to do is be more like me and be less like you."},{"pid":"cb824ae54f1ff807b71a3feaab30dcc7cafb7da2","tid":464642,"uid":137519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"做自己鍾意做既野 但係有時太愛自己 會令身邊既人受傷 要識得拿㘿"},{"pid":"1af5ae37297b8fb19bdef7916a903de04d32202d","tid":464642,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"點先叫愛自己"},{"pid":"212ba0d58ed9a3ead578a1276b56bab122302346","tid":464642,"uid":137519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點先叫愛自己</blockquote><br />\n做既野係為自已開心 咪愛自己囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁簡單都問"},{"pid":"19e9a1bec885600de1e2f7f6c073a931329c9452","ti